{"tid":425269,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"好撚後悔買左switch fifa18","createTime":"2017-10-05T14:43:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-07T06:46:02.000Z","uid":37796,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c405f48562fae8e3878302eec62a29164260102c","tid":425269,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:43:51.000Z","msg":"之前打開fifa17 pc，見佢出switch 版可以同fd係街玩，就入手<br />\n點知隊友ai 比之前更加弱智，走位同之前差唔多冇進步，有時仲會企隊友前面，係度睇隊友扭波都唔撚郁，但防守就弱智左好多<br />\n<br />\n我朋友既分析係：fifa相比winning冇咁流暢，係因為為左令隻game更逼真，每次decision都會多d無謂動作，由你禁制個下開始會delay左少少時間，例如長傳要拉弓，鏟人會delay 一秒，<br />\n今集更加嚴重，所以益左進攻，因為進攻可以早一d做decision(eg. 1-touch pass/射波／推波)，而防守一般要睇左進攻點郁，先可以去做防守decision<br />\n<br />\n我就好同意，同時覺得佢咁好on9 ，同ai打就好明顯，冇人類隊友去協防，好難搶到佢波，只可以等佢傳失波 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有而家3－4－3 盛行既世界，fifa 世界既翼衛同閘位係差唔多企位，進攻個陣，兩個翼衛on99 咁企係中場同中堅平排，較左進攻instruction都係咁 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n進攻方面，除左弱智隊友，直傳又做得差左，傳中又廢，反而扭波就輕鬆左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 整左pro club 同ft 之後隻game冇點樣改善過，淨係識諗點搵錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"92aedf193e8f1d23aa1b84088750b309f7e2299d","tid":425269,"uid":119778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:49:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a710e13662b72d2701bd8aa76a797db0f155b12","tid":425269,"uid":77788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:49:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0ac30579bf2df96e28f00f8e6ffabc0bfb5cc8fd","tid":425269,"uid":37796,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-05T14:50:07.000Z","msg":"switch版又低畫質，陰天球場好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img